column5: Winds are going down, Should be sunny and cool!!!   Good to Go!!  Rick
I might be out sat. Got skunked last week looking for bass
I saw a bit of ice on some puddles this morning....but I don't think Simcoe is ready for walking yet, Rick....I'll wait a few more weeks
~~~~Caught the Flu Bug last weekend on Simcoe, been sick all week, going to stay home in bed this weekend
